title: 100 Million $head
body:
After triple checking all the numbers, it would discovered that 30 million would not be enough to get the games through the first 2 phases of the games. When running the numbers the game will need 100 million $head to cover the initial phases of the game. The vast majority of this $head will go into the hands of the community and be burnt through the game mechanics which will help to make $head more deflationary then initially planned.

So Head DAO community, does Shamdoo have your permission to take 100 million $head tokens in order to fund a game that will provide more value to the $head token and Head DAO NFTs? These $head would come from the 50% that is controlled by the DAO.
